data.description: Charming 2 bed 1.75 bath home with an enclosed sunroom, central AC and heat with a 2 car attached garage is on an extra-large 9716 sq. ft. lot!! The white picket fence on the stone base welcomes you home. Upon entering you are greeted with a large living room that has a view of the mountains from the multiple dual pane windows which let the natural light flow throughout the room. The double-sided brick fireplace between the living room and dining room is perfectly positioned to keep the home warm and cozy on those cold nights. Enjoy cooking in the galley kitchen with beautiful original wood cabinetry along with a china hutch with glass doors to display those special items. Choose to eat in the kitchen nook, breakfast bar or attached dining room that has a ceiling fan centered in the room. The primary bedroom in the back of the home is spacious and has an attached ensuite with a gorgeous floor to ceiling tiled shower. Across the hall is bedroom two that is also very roomy with a ceiling fan and mirrored closet doors. The large hall bath is in the center of the home with a bathtub/shower combination and a vanity with a granite countertop. The enclosed sunroom is an additional space that has a built-in counter, cabinets and small closet for extra storage which is currently being used as a coffee bar and playroom. The sizeable backyard has two patios, one is surrounded by a stone base that has stairs that leading down to the second patio, a stone shed for extra storage and plenty of room for your imagination. The laundry room is in the back of the two-car garage with cabinets above for storing the essentials. Enjoy fresh fruit from the producing mandarin orange, tangelo and avocado trees. Great location….located within the Redlands Unified School District and minutes away from shopping and dining, Redlands University, Crafton Hills College, and the beautiful mountains. Hurry to make your appointment today!!
